thing for you, which is,

00:37:31.450 --> 00:37:34.680
as I told you, that in the
harmonics of the waves,

00:37:34.680 --> 00:37:37.550
the most constant relationship,
aside from the octave,

00:37:37.550 --> 00:37:38.950
is a perfect fifth.

00:37:38.950 --> 00:37:41.410
And that happens purely from
