00:38:15.890 --> 00:38:26.870
[MUSICAL NOTES]

00:38:26.870 --> 00:38:27.380
All right.

00:38:27.380 --> 00:38:29.890
So I just played a
bunch of perfect fifths.

00:38:29.890 --> 00:38:32.560
